title: Whole Foods Market
description: Part of natural foods supermarket chain. Very large space, has fresh fruits and vegetables including organic produce, coffee bar, natural clothing, vitamins, supplements, personal care products, grocery, and more. This WFM has a separate vegan deli in the produce section and also a variety of made to order vegan pizzas. Also deli, hot foods and salad bar with vegan items labeled. Seating inside and out.
